How it works

A fast, transparent process that combines AI speed with human craft.

1. Kickoff

Discovery call, audience & KPI definition, and content brief.

2. Research

Competitive and technical research, citations & interview notes where needed.

3. AI-first draft

Structured drafts produced with controlled models and expert prompt design for speed.

4. Human edit

Polish, accuracy checks and brand voice alignment by an experienced editor.

5. Delivery & measurement

Final assets, SEO guidance, and simple performance tracking suggestions.
